{"tid":1609942,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"從來每一戰都可以係最後一戰","createTime":"2019-10-01T15:54:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-01T16:04:14.000Z","uid":325421,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"fb61836b9c21e25964f4eb068762e4bfe7cd9a05","tid":1609942,"uid":325421,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T15:54:35.000Z","msg":"鬼唔知革命係可以好長？<br />\n但係每一次走上街，目的都係成功。如果唔當每一次都最後一戰，咁同永續社運有乜撚野分別？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">革命是理性的，<br />\n革命中的個體是感性的。<br />\n別總放大革命中單一事件的感性，<br />\n因為革命要成功，必然要有流血，這是走上街前便有的覺悟。</span><br />\n<br />\n中共人禍既時候，好撚中意用單一事件既感性同偉大去掩蓋問題。好似四川大地震咁，當香港向外揭發緊大陸既豆腐渣工程同貪腐既時候，突然就會有個黃福榮，利用單一過體既感性，令大家失去一個big picture.<br />\n<br />\n好明白好多文宣係感性，目的係吸引人關注，所謂核彈核彈，好多時都係情感上可以觸動人既。但係我地係街上，be water 係戰略，心裏應該係堅定既。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n點解戰場上既士兵，明明身邊既人係朝夕相對，大家都知都大家既包袱，但係上到場，所有士兵都唔會即時對身旁人死亡而傷心？<br />\n原因係佢地心裏面明白，士兵代表既係國家，國家輸左，士兵同士兵既包袱，全部都會成為奴隸。<br />\n而家我地為自由而戰，失敗都係為奴，因此，堅決地向前吧，<br />\n<br />\n今日班仆街槍都開撚埋，正式進入戰爭心態啦。<br />\n<br />\n光復香港，時代革命<br />\n<br />\n祝武運亨昌<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"513e69d3dc4d14a09c07abe4b177e83feb64b588","tid":1609942,"uid":325421,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T15:55:08.000Z","msg":"1/10"},{"pid":"954c72e6704cd5f3cddc4684b9c0947d4b0a7f45","tid":1609942,"uid":256281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T15:55:21.000Z","msg":"唔好同我講乜野罷工！同我入黎我解釋你聽<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1609904\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1609904</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"d12491ed85828211fe7eeb730375d6156aa56fd0","tid":1609942,"uid":325421,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T15:55:58.000Z","msg":"2/10"},{"pid":"03b31ecb2f6cbf11e69daf442bfffdb06baf6dd5","tid":1609942,"uid":325421,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T15:57:10.000Z","msg":"今朝想post 但係連登半死<br />\n3/10"},{"pid":"862a31a5c9b3debddb6dbffb44b11175e0ef28bc","tid":1609942,"uid":325421,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T15:58:04.000Z","msg":"4/10"},{"pid":"be1d32948f414f95dd2dc0fce58f60517a28a51c","tid":1609942,"uid":325421,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T15:58:59.000Z","msg":"5/10"},{"pid":"cc62b1ede7e90c04b3d1bf28a7f4cb174b6feba1","tid":1609942,"uid":325421,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T16:00:07.000Z","msg":"6/10"},{"pid":"bc28ff7652a1b77fa9f020831926c05b3061f98c","tid":1609942,"uid":325421,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T16:04:14.000Z","msg":"7/10"}]}